Question: You are given the chance to learn how to play a new instrument. Which one would you choose and why?
Answer:
If I had the chance to play a new instrument, I would learn how to play the drums or a similar percussion instrument. I have always loved the simple but strong beats a drum is able to produce, which probably explains my love for songs with heavy base. The drums provide a strong backbone for a tune and I love how it can carry a song.